'''Eddie Dennis''' (born 22 March 1986) is an Welsh [[professional wrestler]], and former [[head teacher]] from [[Ammanford, Carmarthenshire]]. Originally a [[mathematics]] teacher, Dennis retired from teaching to wrestle full time, most notably for the [[NXT UK]] brand for the [[World Wrestling Entertainment]]. Dennis is a two time heavyweight champion, winning the [[Attack! Pro Wrestling|Attack! championship]], and the [[Pro Wrestling Chaos|King of Chaos]] championship.
