198/tas.2002.s252}}, {{jstor|3087358}}; Steven Byrnes (2007), ''Math. Horizons'' 14 (3): 28, {{jstor|25678674}}.</ref> *{{cite book |last1=Pemmaraju | first1=Sriram |last2=Skiena | first2=Steven | authorlink = <!--Steven Skiena--> |title = Computational Discrete Mathematics: Combinatorics and Graph Theory with Mathematica |publisher = [[Cambridge University Press]] |edition = 1st |isbn = 0-521-12146-9}}<ref>Review of ''Computational Discrete Mathematics'': Martha Patricia Niño Mojica (2005), ''Leonardo'' [https://www.leonardo.info/reviews_archive/feb2005/comp_mojica.html].</ref>
